OL,3,CFans join family and friends of
OL,4,Cmusician Mike Peters at his funeral
OL,6,FFriends, family and fans of musician
OL,7,FMike Peters, who died at the age of
OL,8,F66, gathered in Wales for his funeral
OL,9,Fon Thursday, 29 May.
OL,11,FThe rock star, who was frontman of
OL,12,FWelsh band The Alarm, died on April 29
OL,13,Ffrom blood cancer, more than 30 years
OL,14,Fafter he was first diagnosed with
OL,15,Fchronic lymphocytic leukaemia (CLL) at
OL,16,Fthe age of 36.
