OL,3,CFans join family and friends of
OL,4,Cmusician Mike Peters at his funeral
OL,6,FMore than 150 guests, some who had
OL,7,Ftravelled from the US, attended the
OL,8,Ffuneral service in the village of
OL,9,FDyserth, near Prestatyn, alongside
OL,10,FPeters' wife Jules, 58, and their sons
OL,11,FDylan, 21, and Evan, 18.
OL,13,FIn a statement, Jules Peters said:
OL,14,F"Mike lived as he sang ` with passion,
OL,15,Fcourage, and an unshakeable belief in
OL,16,Fthe power of people to make a
OL,17,Fdifference. His voice may be still,
OL,18,Fbut his message and music will never
OL,19,Ffade.
