OL,3,CFans join family and friends of
OL,4,Cmusician Mike Peters at his funeral
OL,6,F"Mike was so grateful for the love so
OL,7,Fmany people showed him in his
OL,8,Flifetime, and we are so grateful for
OL,9,Fthe outpouring of love our family has
OL,10,Freceived in the past few weeks since
OL,11,Fhe died.
OL,13,F"Mike's music will keep us strong, and
OL,14,Fthe community he built for all of us
OL,15,Fwill sustain us.
OL,17,F"Today is a sad day, but it's also a
OL,18,Fcelebration of his life and the legacy
OL,19,Fhe created. Mike is very much here in
OL,20,Fspirit."
