OL,6,FReverend Gregor Lachlann-Waddell, the
OL,7,Fvicar at the Parish Church of St
OL,8,FBridget and St Cwyfan, said it was an
OL,9,F"honour and a privilege" to lead the
OL,10,Fservice in the village "Mike loved so
OL,11,Fmuch".
OL,13,FHe said: "The celebration we have
OL,14,Fcarefully curated befits a man whose
OL,15,Flife was marked by music, resilience,
OL,16,Fand unwavering hope.
