OL,3,CFans join family and friends of
OL,4,Cmusician Mike Peters at his funeral
OL,6,F"While staying true to his Welsh
OL,7,Froots, Mike found global fame, and the
OL,8,Fpeople who have come to celebrate his
OL,9,Flife today, many travelling thousands
OL,10,Fof miles, are reflective of the
OL,11,Fremarkable life he carved for himself
OL,12,Fand his family."
OL,14,FPeters, who supported U2 and Status
OL,15,FQuo on tour and played with Bob Dylan
OL,16,Fand Bruce Springsteen, underwent
OL,17,Fnumerous drug treatments and rounds of
OL,18,Fchemotherapy, and had tried
OL,19,Fexperimental therapy to keep his
OL,20,Fcancer at bay.
