OL,3,CFans join family and friends of
OL,4,Cmusician Mike Peters at his funeral
OL,6,FLast year, five days before he was due
OL,7,Fto fly to Chicago for a 50-date US
OL,8,Ftour, he noticed that a lump in his
OL,9,Fneck had appeared overnight and
OL,10,Fdoctors quickly realised the star had
OL,11,Fdeveloped Richter's syndrome, where
OL,12,FCLL changes into a much more
OL,13,Faggressive lymphoma.
OL,15,FHe had been undergoing treatment at
OL,16,Fthe Christie NHS Foundation Trust in
OL,17,FManchester before his death. The
OL,18,Fartist first rose to prominence in the
OL,19,Fearly 1980s with The Alarm, with hits
OL,20,Fincluding 68 Guns and Strength.
