OL,3,CFans join family and friends of
OL,4,Cmusician Mike Peters at his funeral
OL,6,FHe was made an MBE in 2019 for
OL,7,Fvoluntary services to cancer care in
OL,8,Fnorth Wales and abroad.
OL,10,FAlongside his wife, he co-founded Love
OL,11,FHope Strength, a cancer charity to
OL,12,Fencourage action around stem cell
OL,13,Fdonation.
OL,15,FThrough its Get On The List campaigns,
OL,16,Foften publicised at rock concerts, the
OL,17,Fcharity has added more than 250,000
OL,18,Fpeople to stem cell registers
OL,19,Fworldwide.
